      <fn id="FN7709177">
        <label>*5</label>
        <p>The Emergy-based approach considers all the inputs used in agricultural production, i.e. natural and anthropogenic inputs. These inputs were converted into a common metric (that is solar equivalent Joule) and then a proportion of natural input is calculated on the total inputs.</p>
